  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero"><div class="wrap">
          <div class="crumb"><a href="/">Home</a> › <a href="/brands/">Brands</a> › Kolpak Walk-In Repair</div>
          <h1>Kolpak Walk-In Cooler &amp; Freezer Repair</h1>
          <p class="lede">
            Kolpak has been the default panel-walk-in spec for new LA restaurants and chain remodels for about fifteen
            years — more Kolpak panels ride in LA back-of-house than any other walk-in brand, full stop. Our techs handle
            Kolpak STIX panel-joint seal work, KCS and KFS indoor-outdoor combo units, P7 outdoor builds, Quick Ship
